{"id":8133,"date":"2021-09-17T07:20:41","date_gmt":"2021-09-17T07:20:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/content\/?page_id=8133"},"modified":"2021-11-07T20:44:06","modified_gmt":"2021-11-07T20:44:06","slug":"yangin-takip","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/uptecra.com\/index.php\/yangin-takip\/","title":{"rendered":"Yang\u0131n Tespit"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row content_text_aligment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1485945943040{padding-top: 104px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1485944455425{padding-top: 0px !important;}&#8221;][vc_row_inner row_content_width=&#8221;grid&#8221; content_text_aligment=&#8221;center&#8221;][vc_column_inner css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1485944381305{padding-top: 0px !important;}&#8221;]<div class=\"edgtf-section-title-holder\" style=\"padding: 0 10%\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"edgtf-st-title\" >\n\t\t\t<span>Yapay Zeka ile Orman Yang\u0131n\u0131 Ba\u015flad\u0131\u011f\u0131nda Nokta Tespiti<\/span>\n\t\t<\/h2>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"edgtf-st-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 30px;margin-top: 21px\">Orman yang\u0131nlar\u0131 hem insanlar hem de vah\u015fi ya\u015fam i\u00e7in \u00f6nemli bir tehdit olu\u015fturur. B\u00fcy\u00fck k\u0131rsal ve vah\u015fi alanlar\u0131 yok ederek b\u00fcy\u00fck can ve mal kayb\u0131na neden olurlar. Bu y\u00fczden bir orman yang\u0131n\u0131 olu\u015fumunu tespit etme yetene\u011fi son derece \u00f6nemlidir. Maalesef bug\u00fcn bir\u00e7ok orman yang\u0131n\u0131 alg\u0131lama sistemi insan g\u00f6zlemi ile yap\u0131lmaktad\u0131r. Bu ise ilgili taraflar\u0131n uyar\u0131lmas\u0131nda gecikmeye neden olur. H\u00fck\u00fcmetlerin yang\u0131nla m\u00fccadele i\u00e7in daha fazla kaynak ay\u0131rmas\u0131na ra\u011fmen ortalama orman yang\u0131n\u0131 boyutu giderek bu sebeplerden artmakta.<\/p>\n\t<\/div><div class=\"edgtf-section-title-holder\" style=\"padding: 0 10%\">\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"edgtf-st-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 30px;margin-top: 21px\">Uptecra Orman Yang\u0131n\u0131 Alg\u0131lama \u00c7\u00f6z\u00fcm\u00fc ise yapay zeka ile 7\/24 g\u00f6rsel ve k\u0131z\u0131l \u00f6tesi analizler ile anl\u0131k olarak yang\u0131n noktas\u0131n\u0131 tespit ederek ilgili nokta bilgisini an\u0131nda ilk m\u00fcdahale ekiplerine ula\u015ft\u0131r\u0131r.<\/p>\n\t<\/div>[\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row content_text_aligment=&#8221;center&#8221; css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1485945943040{padding-top: 104px !important;}&#8221;][vc_column css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1485944455425{padding-top: 0px !important;}&#8221;][vc_row_inner row_content_width=&#8221;grid&#8221; content_text_aligment=&#8221;center&#8221;][vc_column_inner css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1485944381305{padding-top: 0px !important;}&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"full-width.php","meta":{"footnotes":""},"jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/uptecra.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/8133"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/uptecra.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/uptecra.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/uptecra.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/uptecra.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8133"}],"version-history":[{"count":10,"href":"https:\/\/uptecra.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/8133\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8319,"href":"https:\/\/uptecra.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/8133\/revisions\/8319"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/uptecra.com\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8133"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":tru